{"lastModified":1761071423626,"uri":"c::7819249259::vessel::bb629f30-c5b1-11ee-a0a8-4540431682a7","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Tunisia, Italy, France, Greece, Balearic Islands\n\nMIA T-63 Franchini Yachts - Experience the thrill and beauty of our exquisitely crafted sports yacht. This magnificent vessel has been meticulously designed with the environment in mind, using only the finest sustainable materials. With a spacious layout featuring three double, en-suite cabins and a dedicated crew area, every comfort is catered for.The yacht boasts a convenient tender garage located at the stern, ensuring easy access to your water toys. A hydraulic bathing platform adds to the luxury, providing a seamless connection to the sea. For your convenience, the anchor and winch are cleverly concealed, while fender storage keeps everything tidy.\n\nEnjoy ample outdoor areas for relaxation and entertainment on the un-stepped single-level teak deck. This design ensures effortless movement and enhanced safety for all on board. Whether you're sunbathing, dining, or simply taking in the breathtaking views, this yacht offers the perfect setting.\n\nEmbark on an unforgettable journey with the MIA T-63 Franchini Yachts, where excitement meets elegance and luxury meets sustainability.\n","blueprint":{"name":"MIA","images":["/media/media::image::c::7819249259::vessel::bb629f30-c5b1-11ee-a0a8-4540431682a7::assets::88648f10-c5b8-11ee-a0a8-4540431682a7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819249259::vessel::bb629f30-c5b1-11ee-a0a8-4540431682a7::assets::94b37fb0-c5b8-11ee-a0a8-4540431682a7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819249259::vessel::bb629f30-c5b1-11ee-a0a8-4540431682a7::assets::33961e60-c5b6-11ee-a0a8-4540431682a7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819249259::vessel::bb629f30-c5b1-11ee-a0a8-4540431682a7::assets::3397cc10-c5b6-11ee-a0a8-4540431682a7.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819249259::vessel::bb629f30-c5b1-11